# dotctl waybar decorator — pointed (Powerline chevrons)
# This is the canonical form. Canonical console variants ship pointed glyphs,
# so this file is the identity (no substitutions).
#
# Format: each non-comment line is  FROM TO  (whitespace-separated). At apply
# time dotctl reads the file for the active WAYBAR_DECOR and substitutes
# FROM → TO in the waybar config.jsonc.
